Versant is a new project from Carah Faye Charnow, former singer of Shiny Toy Guns. It started towards the end of 2008, with the release some demos in the first half of 2009. They're currently in the studio working on their first album with a planned release for Q4 2009. I encourage anyone who enjoyed Carah's vocals in Shiny Toy Guns to check Versant out and show them your support by buying their album once released.

They've released two demos on their MySpace profile which is the source audio for these files. The demo for Push Away had an embedded watermark inside the track. I've removed this watermark and you won't even notice it was ever there on the included mp3. If there is a desire for these tracks in another format I will upload this again as such.
